{"tid":1506212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日返工放工跳閘啊！","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:43:26.000Z","uid":134854,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7105fd62339d253a36a076630a79e4a38c1a64","tid":1506212,"uid":134854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:31.000Z","msg":"記撚住黨鐵做左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線職員好多黃底<br />\n就算比人捉 就跑走！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日返工放工跳閘啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"696b630e096b7ba27228a96d0adee592b3e2977e","tid":1506212,"uid":134854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:39.000Z","msg":"推啊推啊"},{"pid":"c06dbd53246243212dbed1fdd21396d29e47f104","tid":1506212,"uid":134854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"推啊推啊推啊推啊推啊推啊推啊推啊推啊推啊"},{"pid":"444a82a51cf06c22b0228b98c7bae76ee0b09bd1","tid":1506212,"uid":257447,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:43:03.000Z","msg":"其實「黨鐵」咁樣封半條線，仲要擺明比狗爛運兵車用<br />\n<br />\n會唔會考慮吓呼籲全世界平日返工放工都跳閘<br />\n一兩個人做就會比人搞<br />\n個個都做嘅話點睇？<br />\n文宣會唔會考慮下？<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點先做得起，先講個諗法出嚟<br />\n睇下有冇人做到，呼籲下<br />\n自己人微言輕，唔知點煲大佢<br />\n長者八達通個效果唔明顯<br />\n但跳閘就唔同講法<br />\n又唔洗搵前線打開個閘位，減低前線承受嘅風險，只要肯跳夠多人就做到<br />\n唔單單係星期六日抗爭先做<br />\n係要平日返工放工嘅時候都做<br />\n<br />\n我有呢一個諗法，但唔知點樣煲大佢<br />\n所以先講出嚟睇吓大家有冇D乜嘢諗法"},{"pid":"e20044c41395d8e851ca5df1dc06751782f23ae3","tid":1506212,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:43:17.000Z","msg":"應承你"},{"pid":"f49a4ffa713c33f69dc144817a7efa21442746df","tid":1506212,"uid":40902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"齊齊跳"},{"pid":"34f28cdf8a77e33429123986be9691e056def757","tid":1506212,"uid":134854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r